    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. No unacceptable risks to patient safety identified. Assessment accepted by the credibility assessment team.",
